{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">认识吸热反应。</span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Ba(OH)<sub>2</sub>&middot;8H<sub>2</sub>O+2NH<sub>4</sub>Cl=BaCl<sub>2</sub>+10H<sub>2</sub>O+2NH<sub>3</sub>&uarr;</span></span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">仪器：玻璃片、滴管、药匙、玻璃棒、烧杯。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">药品：八水合氢氧化钡、氯化铵、蒸馏水。</span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">在烧杯中加入20g八水合氢氧化钡和10g氯化铵，并将烧杯放在滴有几滴水的玻璃片上，用玻璃棒搅拌一段时间，拿起烧杯，观察实验现象。</span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">烧杯和玻璃片粘连了。</span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}